Date: 17-19 July 2018 Location: Johannesburg, South Africa Website POWER-GEN & DistribuTECH Africa is the electricity industry’s forum that brings together international business leaders and technical experts committed to POWERING UP A CONTINENT Featuring a comprehensive conference programme and extensive exhibit floor, the event spans all aspects of centralised and distributed power generation along with leading technologies in power transmission and distribution. Put simply, it’s where the industry meets to do business. "The B2B Matchmaking Service provided me with an intense understanding of the companies that I was matched with. My goal was to get international business partners in various respects of our business especially in the projects execution and supply of critical raw materials. I got more than what I wanted and today I am having business discussions with contacts that I got from the B2B Matchmaking Service." 